                            <comment id="17162481" author="ngangam" created="Wed, 22 Jul 2020 05:19:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix has been committed to master. Thank you for the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=Xiaomeng+Zhang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;Xiaomeng Zhang&quot;&gt;Xiaomeng Zhang&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

